ComfyUI-CorridorKey License Notice

This custom node is intended to follow the licensing expectations stated by the
upstream CorridorKey repository by nikopueringer:

https://github.com/nikopueringer/CorridorKey

Summary of the upstream terms as described in the upstream README:

1. The upstream project is not presented as a standard standalone SPDX license
   file. The README describes the release as effectively a variation of
   CC BY-NC-SA 4.0.
2. Repackaging and reselling the tool is not permitted.
3. Offering paid API inference based on the model is not permitted without a
   separate agreement from the upstream author.
4. Released variations or improvements should remain free and open source.
5. Future forks or releases should keep the "Corridor Key" name.

This file is a convenience summary only. The authoritative reference for these
terms is the upstream README section titled:

"CorridorKey Licensing and Permissions"

If the upstream author publishes a formal license file or updated terms, those
terms should be reviewed and this file should be updated accordingly.
